OL,3,CSam Neill's cause of death revealed to
OL,4,Cbe pneumonia
OL,6,FJurassic Park star Sam Neill died from
OL,7,Fpneumonia, his long-time
OL,8,Frepresentative has confirmed.
OL,10,FThe Northern Ireland-born New Zealand
OL,11,Factor, best known for playing Dr Alan
OL,12,FGrant in the blockbuster franchise,
OL,13,Fdied aged 78 in Sydney, Australia, on
OL,14,FMonday.
OL,16,FHis death came months after he
OL,17,Fannounced he was cancer-free following
OL,18,Ftreatment for the "ferocious" and
OL,19,Faggressive form of non-Hodgkin
OL,20,Flymphoma he revealed three years
OL,21,Fearlier.
OL,26,@zD@SOUzD@]O]
