OL,3,CSam Neill's cause of death revealed to
OL,4,Cbe pneumonia
OL,6,FInstead of flowers, his family
OL,7,Frequested donations to the Dunstan
OL,8,FHospital Foundation in New Zealand,
OL,9,Fthe blood cancer research charity the
OL,10,FSnowdome Foundation, or groups working
OL,11,Fto protect New Zealand's flora and
OL,12,Ffauna.
OL,14,FTributes poured in for the actor, who
OL,15,Fwas also known for portraying the
OL,16,Fcorrupt senior police officer Major
OL,17,FChester Campbell in the first two
OL,18,Fseasons of Peaky Blinders opposite
OL,19,FCillian Murphy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
