OL,3,CSam Neill's cause of death revealed to
OL,4,Cbe pneumonia
OL,6,FMurphy paid tribute to Neill, saying:
OL,7,F"Like everyone who knew and worked
OL,8,Fwith Sam, I admired him and adored him
OL,9,Fin equal measure. He was one of the
OL,10,Fkindest, funniest and gentlest people,
OL,11,Fand one of the finest actors...RIP."
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FNeill's Jurassic Park co-stars Laura
OL,19,FDern and Jeff Goldblum were among the
OL,20,Fother celebrities to honour the actor.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
