OL,3,CSam Neill's cause of death revealed to
OL,4,Cbe pneumonia
OL,6,FBorn in Omagh, Northern Ireland, to an
OL,7,FEnglish mother and New Zealand father,
OL,8,FNeill first gained attention for his
OL,9,Frole in the 1977 thriller, Sleeping
OL,10,FDogs.
OL,12,FHis breakthrough came in 1993's
OL,13,FJurassic Park, a franchise he later
OL,14,Freturned to in Jurassic Park III and
OL,15,F2022's Jurassic World Dominion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
